          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>HE Furniture that best doth please</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-2" n="2">S. Patrick's Dean, good Sir, are these;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-3" n="3">The Knife and Fork, with which I eat,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-4" n="4">And next the Pot that boils the Meat;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-5" n="5">The next to be preferred, I think,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-6" n="6">Is the Glass in which I drink;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-7" n="7">The Shelves on which my Books I keep,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-8" n="8">And the Bed in which I sleep;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-9" n="9">An Antique Elbow Chair between,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-10" n="10">Big enough to hold the Dean;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-11" n="11">And the Stove that gives Delight,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-12" n="12">In the cold bleak wintry Night;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-13" n="13">To these we add a Thing below,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-14" n="14">More for Use reserv'd than Shew:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-15" n="15">These are what the Dean do please,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33PK-line-16" n="16">All superfluous are but these.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
